Class ProxyOracleConnection

java.lang.Object
com.stag.identity.shared.config.ProxyOracleConnection
All Implemented Interfaces:
AutoCloseable, Connection, Wrapper
public class ProxyOracleConnection extends Object implements Connection

Proxy Oracle Connection Wrapper

A wrapper for a physical Oracle connection that manages the lifecycle of a proxy session. It delegates all calls to the physical connection but intercepts the close() call to ensure the proxy session is terminated before the physical connection is returned to the pool. This prevents proxy session leaks in connection pooling scenarios.

Version:
1.0.0
Author:
Jakub Pavlíček
